<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.964.55703.figures4-8>
    dc:description "Figures 4 - 8. Habitus of Nagiella species 4 N. hortulatoides male 5 N. inferior male 6 N. quadrimaculalis male 7 Nagia incomitata Swinhoe 1894 female, type, BMNH Pyr., London. 7 A head 8 Nagiella bispina sp. nov. male, holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/446787" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.964.55703.figures9-15>
    dc:description "Figures 9 - 15. Genitalia of Nagiella species 9 N. hortulatoides: male, genitalia slide no. LXQ 18311 10, 13 N. inferior: 10 male, genitalia slide no. LXQ 18291 13 female, genitalia slide no. XLJ 14239 11, 14 N. quadrimaculalis: 11 male, genitalia slide no. LXQ 18310 14 female, genitalia slide no. LXQ 18306 12, 15 N. bispina sp. nov.: 12 male, holotype, genitalia slide no. XLJ 14011 15 female, paratype, slide no. XLJ 14009 15 A signa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/446788" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.964.55703.figures2-3>
    dc:description "Figures 2, 3. Head and wing venation of Nagiella quadrimaculalis (Kollar & Redtenbacher, 1844). Wing slide no. LXQ 20001, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/446786" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

